255
00:22:36,309 --> 00:22:48,178
[SPEAKER_16]: I was impressed with all that and thought that all that was really great from my experience working in high school spaces, but also just hearing how much a bummer it is to get from one class to the other in the current space.

256
00:22:49,259 --> 00:23:02,370
[SPEAKER_16]: At what point does the rough estimate of hallway and passing space combined with the various volumes of tall versus wide really start to force

257
00:23:03,618 --> 00:23:21,005
