279
00:26:03,661 --> 00:26:08,545
[SPEAKER_01]: Personally, I don't really have any fear about that, only because what we're using is a fairly

280
00:26:09,807 --> 00:26:24,657
[SPEAKER_01]: Industry standard, industry being sort of the MSBA process of what we're doing of using that 1.5 multiplier of looking at the usable square footage to that grossing factor square footage, the hallways, the toilet rooms, mechanical spaces, et cetera.

281
00:26:25,858 --> 00:26:31,462
[SPEAKER_01]: We have both SOMA as well as every other designer that is working through the MSBA grant program.

282
00:26:32,222 --> 00:26:35,426
[SPEAKER_01]: has a pretty common practice of working with that 1.5 multiplier.

283
00:26:35,626 --> 00:26:44,755
[SPEAKER_01]: And we know that we can come up with a facility that will satisfy the educational plan using that sort of balance and that multiplier.

284
00:26:44,815 --> 00:26:47,638
[SPEAKER_01]: So we have a high level of confidence there.

