[SPEAKER_13]: Lisa.

1212
01:37:05,154 --> 01:37:25,332
[SPEAKER_09]: I just had a question because I'm not sure where this would fit in, but like the traffic flow at the school, I know that there's one of these that says separates safe circulation of the bus, vehicle, pedestrian, and bike access, but kind of the circulation of cars at the school is more than just the separation.

1213
01:37:26,293 --> 01:37:36,281
[SPEAKER_09]: And I wasn't sure if there should be some something that addresses that, especially the the entering and exiting the 20 minute wait to get out of the school at the end of the day.

1214
01:37:36,301 --> 01:37:41,085
[SPEAKER_09]: I'm not sure that that's included anywhere, or if it's appropriate.

1215
01:37:42,986 --> 01:37:43,306
