[SPEAKER_01]: An item under 7 that would say improves on site.

1218
01:37:55,122 --> 01:37:58,484
[SPEAKER_01]: traffic circulation to address it.

1219
01:37:58,524 --> 01:38:09,269
[SPEAKER_01]: I mean, you could argue that offsite traffic impact, that's really going to deal with sort of the delay, the lag in terms of getting into the site or egressing in the afternoon.

1220
01:38:10,070 --> 01:38:18,914
[SPEAKER_01]: But I think your point, Lisa, about circulating on the site doesn't seem like it's captured currently in any of the other site items.

1221
01:38:18,954 --> 01:38:22,556
[SPEAKER_01]: I'm not sure if there was anything earlier that touched on it.

1222
01:38:24,822 --> 01:38:28,165
[SPEAKER_01]: No, so I think it would be a potential to add 7.7.

1223
01:38:31,167 --> 01:38:34,369
